messages.text: You awake?
Yeah, who can sleep ☹
Can’t believe Roxy’s gone.
I thought we’d always be together.  Three Muska-tiaras….
I have, like, 9 voice mails on here from her, I can’t erase them OR listen to them.
I know, we’ll get through this together.
Randall’s been a big help, of course.
Yeah, sometimes guys can be big insensitive donkeys, lol, but he’s cool.
Wow, a cool boyfriend that a mother likes?  Marry him!
God, I feel this big empty space inside of me.  I guess that’s Roxy.  Roxy has been taken from me and now I have all this….empty space.
But somebody’s gotta do something.  She’d do it for us.
Yeah…should I wear my pink pajamas or my orange pajamas?
What does Randall prefer?
He thinks I’m Pretty in Pink.
So go Orange.  Always leave them a little frustrated.  He’s gotta earn Pink.
Oh he earns it….lol
Say, what about that heavy metal guy?  Slag?
Sven?
Yeah him.  Didn’t he try to pick her up and she told him to get lost?
Yeah, I dunno, he didn’t make a big deal out of it…
yeah but he’s kinda weird
Oh he just wears the Goth uniform, he’s all right….

I mean last week, on Tuesday, when she didn’t show up for her shift at Claire’s…he didn’t show up at the FYE.  I asked Barry, from the Sunglass Hut?  Sven definitely wasn’t there, he always works register on Tuesdays.
Roxy didn’t show up for work Tuesday night?
No, I mean, she called in advance, it wasn’t that weird, except she never misses work.
You were there that night?
Yeah, it was a slow night, wasn’t a big deal anyway.
But I saw her that night.
Yeah?
She was wearing earrings, those adorable little gold ones with the unicorns on them that you guys got in…
Oh yeah she liked those.
But she said she picked them up at work.
Maybe she meant some other day.
No, she came home around eleven – I remember it was exactly eleven – I was on the porch and my dad was watching the news inside, I heard the music
OK
And she came home.  She said she came home from work, and showed me the earrings.  Said you guys just got a shipment that night.
I don’t know, I know she wasn’t there, but maybe it’s no big deal.
And maybe she wasn’t found dead on the corner with a brick embedded in her skull, Lena!
Jesus, Amy.
She’s dead and we’re alive and it doesn’t seem fair.  Everything’s important!  She was out Tuesday night!  She didn’t tell me the truth about what she was doing.
Well, like I said, Sven wasn’t at the mall either.  He did get suspended once for cursing out the Chemistry teacher…
Yeah, I mean I’ve known him since I was, like, six, I don’t think of him like that.
And he’s so weird, he’s so into that “Dad” music.  Those Led Zep t-shirts, he’s always singing that “Smells like Teen Angst” song…
Oh.  My.  God.
What?
“Smells Like Teen Spirit.”
Jesus, Amy, whatever!
No, Roxy was singing that when she came home Tuesday, I remember, I thought it was weird cuz six days a week she’s all Ariana Grande and then suddenly she’s somber rock?
You think Roxy and Sven were together?
I don’t know, but she wasn’t at work, she lied about getting the earrings that night, she was up to something!
She was secretly seeing Sven! OMG.
That doesn’t mean he killed her, Lena, let’s keep it real.
You know he’s got nunchucks and all that.  He thinks he’s Bruce Lee.
One Sec.  Randall is here.
Tell him I said Hi.
He’s warming up some pierogis in the kitchen that he got at the Polish diner.
He knows your taste.
I mean, aren’t we driving each other a little crazy? My next door neighbor is dead, and we’re blaming my other next door neighbor for killing her!
I never trusted him.  Sven’s got beady eyes and that stringy long blond hair and his sullen look…
Yeah, I always found him kind of cute. Anyway, you said Sven asked her out and she said no. Why say no if she was seeing him?  She’s single, if she was seeing him, it could be public…
I dunno.  Maybe her parents wouldn’t approve of him. Mine wouldn’t
So she already had those earrings. You didn’t get a shipment in on Tuesday.
No, we did.
But you had them in stock before.
No, they were in the catalog, remember?  We were all looking in the catalog at the preorders and agreed they were 2 die 4.
Yeah, yeah, I liked them too.  I still like them, although now they just make me sad if I think about them.
Well, what are you gonna do with your pair?
My pair?
Yeah, I think you should wear them.  Roxy would want it.
I don’t have a pair, Lena, what are you talking about?  You said the shipment just came in on Tuesday.  I haven’t been there since last month.
No, but Randall came in and got them for you.
What?  When?
When, Lena?
Tuesday night.  He came in and bought them, I smiled at him.  He was wearing that blue shirt you like.
Tuesday night?  He was working Tuesday at The Burger Baron.
He was?
That’s what he told me.
He was at the mall.  He bought the earrings, right after we unpacked them.
He was wearing the blue shirt?  The button down Navy blue? The one he is wearing tonight?
That’s what he wore, yeah.
He didn’t buy those earrings for me…
I don’t know…
Hold on.
You don’t think Randall and Roxy…
Amy?
Cl the Polic
Oh god, what? I don’t believe this
Amy?
10 minutes later…
Lena?
OMG OMG Amy?
Apparently Randall bought them for Roxy, Lena.
What happened?  What the hell just happened?
Um, they’ve been seeing each other behind my back, Lena.
OMG
When I confronted him, he got all crazy.  Just started letting it spill out.  In front of mom, even.  Roxy told him she was pregnant, he responded with a brick to her head.
Oh god, what happened, are you OK?
Randall just chased me and my mom around the house with a steak knife, I went out my window into the backyard…
But you’re OK.  You’re OK! You’re talking to me now!  What happened?
Well. Lucky for me.  Sven was nearby with his nunchucks.
